com.gwtplatform.crawlerservice.server
Annotation Type HtmlUnitTimeoutMillis

@Target(value={FIELD,PARAMETER,METHOD})
@Retention(value=RUNTIME)
public @interface HtmlUnitTimeoutMillis

Use this annotation to indicate how long HtmlUnit should pump the javascript event loop before timing out. Use in your AbstractModule with a call to bindConstant().annotatedWith(HtmlUnitTimeout.class).to(10000).

Author:
Philippe Beaudoin
